728
00:41:34,910 --> 00:41:38,220
*Because to tell you the truth *

729
00:41:38,290 --> 00:41:41,710
*I'll be lonely *

730
00:41:42,390 --> 00:41:44,100
*I don't mind *

731
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:48,260
*Being lonely *

732
00:41:48,330 --> 00:41:52,670
